name: Miscellaneous Industrial Mineral Operations , USA
description: This map layer includes miscellaneous industrial minerals operations in the United States.  The data represent commodities covered by the Minerals Information Team (MIT) of the U.S. Geological Survey.  The mineral operations are plants and (or) mines surveyed by the MIT and considered currently active in 2003.  This is a replacement for the July 2004 map layer.Industrial Mineral Operations in the US. this data is shown as point level data for the United States. data was found at the National Atlas, URL: www.nationalatlas.gov
